## 3. Threshold objective (AC #12 — precision-first)

Winner rule = **max coverage** s.t. **verified_precision ≥ {{precision_floor}}**
(auto-apply precision floor) AND **none_false_apply ≤ {{none_ceiling}}** (false-apply
ceiling). `T_declared` tuned for Stage-2 handoff recall. macro-F1 **not** used (equal
cost to false-apply/miss → rejected). Floor/ceiling pinned here from the sweep.

- Achieved at winner: coverage `{{coverage}}` · verified_precision
  `{{verified_precision}}` · none_false_apply `{{none_false_apply}}` · macro_f1
  `{{macro_f1}}` (reported).

